==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wallerian degeneration
<hw>Wal*le"ri*an de*gen`er*a"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>A form of degeneration occurring in nerve fibers as a result of
their division; -- so called from Dr. <ets>Waller</ets>, who published
an account of it in 1850.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wallet</ent>⟦br⟧
